casebody.data:
Terry STRICKLAND, et al., Appellants,
v.
Charles STATHAM, et al., Respondents. WD 82098 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. Order filed: July 23, 2019 Nicky McNeil, Co-counsel for Appellants David A. Gellis, Kansas City, for Respondents Before Division Three: Gary D. Witt, Presiding Judge, Edward R. Ardini, Jr., Judge and Tom N. Chapman, Judge

ORDER

PER CURIAM:

Terry and Angela Strickland appeal an order of the Circuit Court of Jackson County granting summary judgment in favor of Charles and Carol Statham. Finding no error, we affirm. Because a published opinion would have no precedential value, a memorandum of law has been provided to the parties. Rule 84.16(b).
